---
title: Chipotle Beef & Black Bean Tacos with Charred Corn Slaw & Plant-Based Mayo
description: Transform black beans and beef into something special by cooking them with our Tex-Mex spice blend and mild chipotle sauce. Stuff the bean mixture into warm flour tortillas, top with a creamy slaw and dinner is done!

*Unfortunately, this week's
shredded cabbage was
in short supply, so we've
replaced it with slaw mix.
Don't worry, the recipe
will be just as delicious,
just be sure to follow your
recipe card!*
